{"step_index":12,"source":"MODEL","type":"VIEW_FILE","status":"DONE","created_at":"2026-07-18T06:42:07Z","content":"Created At: 2026-07-18T13:42:07+07:00\nCompleted At: 2026-07-18T13:42:07+07:00\nFile Path: `file:///home/hieu/Downloads/Code/VAIC%202026/v-nexus/.env.example`\nTotal Lines: 27\nTotal Bytes: 677\nShowing lines 1 to 27\nThe following code has been modified to include a line number before every line, in the format: <line_number>: <original_line>. Please note that any changes targeting the original code should remove the line number, colon, and leading space.\n1: # --- LLM Mode: \"fpt\" (cloud) | \"ollama\" (local) | \"offline\" (template fallback) ---\n2: LLM_MODE=fpt\n3: \n4: # --- FPT AI Inference (OpenAI-compatible) ---\n5: API_KEY=\n6: LLM_BASE_URL=https://mkp-api.fptcloud.com/v1\n7: LLM_MODEL=GLM-5.2\n8: \n9: # --- Ollama (local, dùng khi LLM_MODE=ollama) ---\n10: OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://ollama:11434/v1\n11: OLLAMA_MODEL=qwen3:1.7b\n12: \n13: # --- PostgreSQL ---\n14: POSTGRES_USER=vnexus\n15: POSTGRES_PASSWORD=vnexus\n16: POSTGRES_DB=vnexus\n17: DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://vnexus:vnexus@db:5432/vnexus\n18: \n19: # --- MCP Server mẫu ---\n20: MCP_SERVER_URL=http://mcp_server:8100/mcp\n21: \n22: # --- Frontend -> Gateway ---\n23: GATEWAY_URL=http://gateway:8000\n24: \n25: # --- Auth (JWT) ---\n26: AUTH_SECRET=change-me-dev-only-secret\n27: \nThe above content shows the entire, complete file contents of the requested file.\n"}
