{"step_index":70,"source":"MODEL","type":"PLANNER_RESPONSE","status":"DONE","created_at":"2026-07-18T09:41:06Z","content":"I will rewrite [agent/llm_client.py](file:///home/hieu/Downloads/Code/VAIC%202026/v-nexus/agent/llm_client.py) to update `create_message_fpt` to use the new settings, add `create_message_ollama()`, `call_llm()`, and `is_llm_available()`.","thinking":"**Analyzing the Agent Setup**\n\nI've successfully identified where the LLM model is configured for the planner agent. Specifically, in `gateway/app/routes/chat.py`, the agent is instantiated with a model pulled from `settings.llm_model`, which is configured in `gateway/app/config.py`. This config grabs an environment variable \"LLM_MODEL\".\n\n\n**Updating the LLM Client**\n\nI've confirmed the `llm_model` setting is correctly mapped in `gateway/app/config.py`. Now, I'm refactoring `agent/llm_client.py`. Specifically, I'm updating the `create_message_fpt` function to use `settings.llm_base_url`, `settings.api_key`, and `settings.llm_model` instead of the deprecated FPT-specific settings, ensuring compatibility with the new LLM configuration. This is key to ensuring the LLM client works with different models.\n\n\n","tool_calls":[{"name":"replace_file_content","args":{"AllowMultiple":"false","Description":"\"Update agent/llm_client.py with the dispatcher and Ollama / connection checking methods.\"","EndLine":"72","Instruction":"\"Replace create_message_fpt and add create_message_ollama, call_llm, and is_llm_available.\"","ReplacementContent":"\"def create_message_fpt(*, system: str, messages: list[dict], tools: list[dict] = None, model: str = None):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Gọi FPT AI Inference (OpenAI-compatible chat completions).\\n\\n    Trả về dict: {\\\"text\\\": str, \\\"tool_calls\\\": [{\\\"name\\\", \\\"input\\\"}]} để Planner Agent\\n    (hoặc tool trực tiếp) dễ sử dụng. Nếu không có tool_call thì chỉ có text.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    from openai import OpenAI\\n\\n    client = OpenAI(base_url=settings.llm_base_url, api_key=settings.api_key, timeout=30.0)\\n    req_model = model or settings.llm_model\\n\\n    openai_tools = None\\n    if tools:\\n        openai_tools = [\\n            {\\n                \\\"type\\\": \\\"function\\\",\\n                \\\"function\\\": {\\n                    \\\"name\\\": t[\\\"name\\\"],\\n                    \\\"description\\\": t.get(\\\"description\\\", \\\"\\\"),\\n                    \\\"parameters\\\": t.get(\\\"input_schema\\\", t.get(\\\"parameters\\\", {})),\\n                },\\n            }\\n            for t in tools\\n        ]\\n\\n    completion = client.chat.completions.create(\\n        model=req_model,\\n        messages=[{\\\"role\\\": \\\"system\\\", \\\"content\\\": system}, *messages],\\n        tools=openai_tools,\\n        tool_choice=\\\"auto\\\" if openai_tools else None,\\n        temperature=0.3,\\n    )\\n    choice = completion.choices[0].message\\n\\n    text = choice.content or \\\"\\\"\\n    tool_calls = []\\n    if getattr(choice, \\\"tool_calls\\\", None):\\n        for tc in choice.tool_calls:\\n            import json\\n\\n            try:\\n                args = json.loads(tc.function.arguments or \\\"{}\\\")\\n            except Exception:\\n                args = {}\\n            tool_calls.append({\\\"name\\\": tc.function.name, \\\"input\\\": args})\\n\\n    return {\\\"text\\\": text, \\\"tool_calls\\\": tool_calls}\\n\\n\\ndef create_message_ollama(*, system: str, messages: list[dict], tools: list[dict] = None, model: str = None):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Gọi Ollama (OpenAI-compatible chat completions).\\n\\n    Trả về dict: {\\\"text\\\": str, \\\"tool_calls\\\": [{\\\"name\\\", \\\"input\\\"}]}\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    from opena\n<truncated 2960 bytes>","StartLine":"25","TargetContent":"\"def create_message_fpt(*, system: str, messages: list[dict], tools: list[dict] = None, model: str = None):\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"Gọi FPT AI Inference (OpenAI-compatible chat completions).\\n\\n    Trả về dict: {\\\"text\\\": str, \\\"tool_calls\\\": [{\\\"name\\\", \\\"input\\\"}]} để Planner Agent\\n    (hoặc tool trực tiếp) dễ sử dụng. Nếu không có tool_call thì chỉ có text.\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    from openai import OpenAI\\n\\n    client = OpenAI(base_url=settings.fpt_api_base, api_key=settings.fpt_api_key, timeout=30.0)\\n    req_model = model or settings.fpt_model\\n\\n    openai_tools = None\\n    if tools:\\n        openai_tools = [\\n            {\\n                \\\"type\\\": \\\"function\\\",\\n                \\\"function\\\": {\\n                    \\\"name\\\": t[\\\"name\\\"],\\n                    \\\"description\\\": t.get(\\\"description\\\", \\\"\\\"),\\n                    \\\"parameters\\\": t.get(\\\"input_schema\\\", t.get(\\\"parameters\\\", {})),\\n                },\\n            }\\n            for t in tools\\n        ]\\n\\n    completion = client.chat.completions.create(\\n        model=req_model,\\n        messages=[{\\\"role\\\": \\\"system\\\", \\\"content\\\": system}, *messages],\\n        tools=openai_tools,\\n        tool_choice=\\\"auto\\\" if openai_tools else None,\\n        temperature=0.3,\\n    )\\n    choice = completion.choices[0].message\\n\\n    text = choice.content or \\\"\\\"\\n    tool_calls = []\\n    if getattr(choice, \\\"tool_calls\\\", None):\\n        for tc in choice.tool_calls:\\n            import json\\n\\n            try:\\n                args = json.loads(tc.function.arguments or \\\"{}\\\")\\n            except Exception:\\n                args = {}\\n            tool_calls.append({\\\"name\\\": tc.function.name, \\\"input\\\": args})\\n\\n    return {\\\"text\\\": text, \\\"tool_calls\\\": tool_calls}\"","TargetFile":"\"/home/hieu/Downloads/Code/VAIC 2026/v-nexus/agent/llm_client.py\"","toolAction":"\"Rewriting llm_client.py\"","toolSummary":"\"Rewriting llm_client.py\""}}],"truncated_fields":["tool_calls"]}
{"step_index":71,"source":"MODEL","type":"CODE_ACTION","status":"DONE","created_at":"2026-07-18T09:41:14Z","content":"Created At: 2026-07-18T16:41:14+07:00\nCompleted At: 2026-07-18T16:41:34+07:00\nThe following changes were made by the replace_file_content tool to: /home/hieu/Downloads/Code/VAIC 2026/v-nexus/agent/llm_client.py. If relevant, proactively run terminal commands to execute this code for the USER. Don't ask for permission.\n[diff_block_start]\n@@ -30,43 +30,132 @@\n     \"\"\"\n     from openai import OpenAI\n \n-    client = OpenAI(base_url=settings.fpt_api_base, api_key=settings.fpt_api_key, timeout=30.0)\n-    req_model = model or settings.fpt_model\n-\n-    openai_tools = None\n-    if tools:\n-        openai_tools = [\n-            {\n-                \"type\": \"function\",\n-                \"function\": {\n-                    \"name\": t[\"name\"],\n-                    \"description\": t.get(\"description\", \"\"),\n-                    \"parameters\": t.get(\"input_schema\", t.get(\"parameters\", {})),\n-                },\n-            }\n-            for t in tools\n-        ]\n-\n-    completion = client.chat.completions.create(\n-        model=req_model,\n-        messages=[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": system}, *messages],\n-        tools=openai_tools,\n-        tool_choice=\"auto\" if openai_tools else None,\n-        temperature=0.3,\n-    )\n-    choice = completion.choices[0].message\n-\n-    text = choice.content or \"\"\n-    tool_calls = []\n-    if getattr(choice, \"tool_calls\", None):\n-        for tc in choice.tool_calls:\n-            import json\n-\n-            try:\n-                args = json.loads(tc.function.arguments or \"{}\")\n-            except Exception:\n-                args = {}\n-            tool_calls.append({\"name\": tc.function.name, \"input\": args})\n-\n-    return {\"text\": text, \"tool_calls\": tool_calls}\n+    client = OpenAI(base_url=settings.llm_base_url, api_key=settings.api_key, timeout=30.0)\n+    req_model = model or settings.llm_model\n+\n+    openai_tools = None\n+    if tools:\n+        openai_tools = [\n+            {\n+                \"type\": \"function\",\n+                \"function\": {\n+                    \"name\": t[\"name\"],\n+                  \n<truncated 2289 bytes>\n  args = json.loads(tc.function.arguments or \"{}\")\n+            except Exception:\n+                args = {}\n+            tool_calls.append({\"name\": tc.function.name, \"input\": args})\n+\n+    return {\"text\": text, \"tool_calls\": tool_calls}\n+\n+\n+def call_llm(*, system: str, messages: list[dict], tools: list[dict] = None, model: str = None):\n+    \"\"\"Bộ điều phối (dispatcher) cuộc gọi LLM dựa trên LLM_MODE.\"\"\"\n+    mode = (settings.llm_mode or \"offline\").lower()\n+    if mode == \"fpt\":\n+        return create_message_fpt(system=system, messages=messages, tools=tools, model=model)\n+    elif mode == \"ollama\":\n+        return create_message_ollama(system=system, messages=messages, tools=tools, model=model)\n+    elif mode == \"offline\":\n+        raise RuntimeError(\"LLM is configured in offline mode.\")\n+    else:\n+        raise ValueError(f\"Unknown LLM mode: {settings.llm_mode}\")\n+\n+\n+def is_llm_available() -> bool:\n+    \"\"\"Kiểm tra xem LLM hiện tại có thể kết nối được không.\"\"\"\n+    mode = (settings.llm_mode or \"offline\").lower()\n+    if mode == \"offline\":\n+        return False\n+\n+    import requests\n+\n+    if mode == \"fpt\":\n+        if not settings.api_key:\n+            return False\n+        try:\n+            url = f\"{settings.llm_base_url.rstrip('/')}/models\"\n+            headers = {\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {settings.api_key}\"}\n+            r = requests.get(url, headers=headers, timeout=3.0)\n+            return r.status_code == 200\n+        except Exception:\n+            return False\n+    elif mode == \"ollama\":\n+        try:\n+            url = f\"{settings.ollama_base_url.rstrip('/')}/models\"\n+            r = requests.get(url, timeout=3.0)\n+            return r.status_code == 200\n+        except Exception:\n+            return False\n+    return False\n \n[diff_block_end]\n\nPlease note that the above snippet only shows the MODIFIED lines from the last change. It shows up to 3 lines of unchanged lines before and after the modified lines. The actual file contents may have many more lines not shown.","truncated_fields":["content"]}
