{"step_index":5,"source":"MODEL","type":"PLANNER_RESPONSE","status":"DONE","created_at":"2026-07-18T14:49:17Z","thinking":"**Analyzing the Prompt Plan**\n\nI'm currently reviewing the prompt optimization plan located at `/home/hieu/Downloads/Code/VAIC 2026/v-nexus/domain.md`. My focus is on understanding the proposed strategies and their potential impact. I'm taking a close look at the structure and techniques described. Specifically, I am trying to determine the quality of the prompts described.\n\n\n**Evaluating the Optimization Proposal**\n\nI've delved deeper into the `/home/hieu/Downloads/Code/VAIC 2026/v-nexus/domain.md` document, focusing on the prompt optimization strategy. The core idea of recommending diverse pathways to teachers is solid, triggered by data analysis. I'm assessing the three distinct strategic axes, and the separate LLM calls. It all sounds pretty good. I am carefully considering the fixed skeleton approach, and the other techniques listed. The reliability techniques seem like a nice touch. I'm keen to test these aspects.\n\n\n**Revising the Assessment Framework**\n\nI am now focused on refining our plan review. I'm examining its strengths, like the logical data trigger and the teacher-in-the-loop design. I'm especially focused on the points for improvement, particularly the latency concerns from the 3 LLM calls. The priority matrix is interesting. I'm also considering the AI safety emphasis. I'm working on how to best measure similarity in the code-level duplicate checks, to ensure we find true strategic overlap.\n\n\n**Refining the Feedback Structure**\n\nI'm now restructuring the feedback to address teacher cognitive load, grounding verification, and BKT Engine integration. I'll include a summary table suggestion. I'm also planning to use schema validation for strict grounding and explore providing only local subgraphs for the LLM. Finally, I'm thinking of creating a draft template and incorporating system instructions and few-shot examples for prompt design. I've decided to write the feedback in Vietnamese.\n\n\n","tool_calls":[{"name":"list_dir","args":{"DirectoryPath":"\"/home/hieu/Downloads/Code/VAIC 2026/v-nexus\"","toolAction":"\"Listing project directory\"","toolSummary":"\"List project directory\""}}]}
